{
  "stem": "4710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- it was-- you could see from the faces of the people who escaped that it's something horrible going on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my cousin, who was-- who must have been in his 20s, who escaped, and he knew that his parents had been taken away and he's the only one who managed to get-- to get out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Little bits of stories and from schoolmates, all the people who-- all the [INAUDIBLE] who were older than me and they came-- those who were already in Budapest, they came down and they-- they were more-- more knowledgeable.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was really very aware of it, in fact, more than my schoolmates, somehow, I feel, because I was somehow-- I-- I don't want to brag about that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was really older than my age.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always felt that I'm-- I'm a-- I'm grown up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Possibly-- possibly these kind of circumstances which we found ourselves in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Possibly they knew about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But somehow-- somehow, this kind of subject, it was not discussed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we have to pretend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In order to carry on living, you had to pretend that living from day to day, everything is all right for the time being.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is a-- this was a half an hour?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The schooling went on right-- right almost until the Germans moved into Hungary in 1944.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no changes in the-- in the curriculum.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were still-- still studying the greatness of our country Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I realized it by that time, especially when our regular teacher was called in into-- into military service, or rather this labor service, which I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a substitute teacher who taught us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
